summary: - This is a mod that gives you a Wood Elf boy to adopt.
descriptionHtml:
This is a mod that gives you a Wood Elf boy to adopt. He replaces Alesan, the Redguard child from Dawnstar. 

NOTE: This mod requires Dawnguard and Hearthfire. Jurenil has some Dawnguard items in his inventory, that\'s why DG is required.
As stated above, he is located in Dawnstar.

Thank you for downloading this mod, and if you like it, remember to endorse it!

Cheers,
  pwner69.
author: Pwner 69
